Requirements :
- mongodb http://mongodb.org
- node.js http://nodejs.org/

node modules:
- express 
- jade
- jquery
- mongodb
- stylus

Install npm to get the above packages. http://npmjs.org/
 
use "npm install package_name" to install in the checked out dir.


To run:
node app.js

Make sure that you have installed mongodb for your platform and it is running.